(31, 'four_wheel', 12, 0, 'uploads/d8bf6a3177420bc0763f383130c64011.jpg', 'The Ferrari F8 Spider â€“ The Evolution Of The Species', 1, 'News', 'Edit Oleh Preibu.', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/b52ea92682902fdc45fdfe4caf2cb242.jpg', 'uploads/86cf3113913cc870511103cc517d8ade.jpg', 'uploads/2ca53081df5903729e52e8818cd84974.jpg', 'null', 'The mid-rear-engined drop-top powered by the most successful Ferrari V8 ever\n\nFerrari has unveiled the F8 Spider, the new generation drop-top sports car equipped with the most successful mid-rear-mounted V8 in history.', 'The Ferrari F8 Spider was designed in parallel with the F8 Tributo berlinetta and features the Prancing Horseâ€™s compact and efficient RHT (Retractable Hard Top) which influences the lines of a model that leads its category.\n\nThe F8 Spider is the latest addition to an exclusive and prestigious bloodline of open-top V8 cars begun with the 308 GTS in 1977. It is less extreme than the 488 Pista Spider, but sportier than the 488 Spider which it replaces in the range.\n\nConsequently, the F8 Spider sets a new benchmark for the â€œen plein airâ€ sports car in terms of usable performance and exceptional handling, providing an incredibly rewarding driving experience.\n\nThe Ferrari spider thus combines the characteristics of the most lauded 8-cylinder engine in history with unparalleled driving pleasure.\n\nThe V8 has raised the performance bar to unprecedented new heights, not only for turbo engines but power units of all types. The engine is a development of the V8 that won the â€œInternational Engine of the Year Awardâ€ for four consecutive years (2016, 2017, 2018 and 2019) and that was also selected as the best engine of the last two decades.\n\n\n\nThe mission of every new model produced by Maranello is to introduce new design features and outperform its predecessors on all fronts. The challenge the engineers and designers always face is to push their own creative limits and the boundaries of technology by introducing new, leading-edge solutions and setting new levels of excellence. This is something they have done to brilliant effect once again with this new model.\n\nThe F8 Spider replaces the 488 Spider and improves on all aspects of its specifications: aside from the fact that its engine delivers an extra 50 cv, the new Ferrari is 20 kg lighter than its predecessor.\n\nIt weighs just 20 kg more than the more extreme 488 Pista Spider. The F8 Spider is significantly more aerodynamically efficient, too and features the new 6.1 version of the Side Slip Angle Control system.\n\nENGINE\n\nIn the automotive world, Ferrariâ€™s V8 engine is seen as the very epitome of sportiness and driving pleasure. This is particularly the case when it is mid-rear-mounted in a two-seater.\n\nThe V8â€™s technical specifications are truly exceptional. The 3902 cc unit unleashes 720 cv at 8,000 rpm and also has an impressive specific power output of 185 cv/l. Its maximum torque is now higher at all engine speeds, peaking at 770 Nm at 3,250 rpm.\n\n\n\nInstantaneously accessible power is matched by exceptional handling thanks to advanced vehicle dynamics solutions.\n\nThese include a new version of the Ferrari Dynamic Enhancer (FDE+) which can now\nbe activated in the manettinoâ€™s RACE position, a move designed to make performance on the limit easier to reach and control.\n\nTo achieve the 50 cv increase in power compared to the 488 Spider, the new intake line is derived directly from the 488 Challenge. In the F8 Spider, the air intakes have been moved from the flanks to the rear where they are located on either side of the blown spoiler and are directly connected to the intake plenums.\n\nThis drastically reduces losses and ensures greater air flow to the engine, thereby increasing the power. The air flow also benefits from increased dynamic pressure created by the shape of the rear spoiler.\n\nAdaptive Performance Launch analyses grip as the car accelerates and then uses electronic controls to optimise the torque delivered to suit the roadâ€™s grip level, reducing wheel slip to a minimum which, in turn, maximises acceleration.\n\nThe rev limiterâ€™s â€œWall Effectâ€ strategy is another leap forward in terms of extreme engine performance. Rather than gradually limiting the revs towards the limit, it cuts off right at the 8,000 rpm red-line, maximising the amount of power available in power-on dynamic driving situations and consequently improving lap times.\n\n\n\nAdopted once again on this model is the hugely successful Ferrari Variable Torque Management strategy for all gears. To adapt it to the carâ€™s extreme sporty spirit, all of the torque curves were redesigned to deliver a feeling of consistently smooth, powerful acceleration all the way to the red line.\n\nMaximum torque is 10 Nm higher than on the 488 Spider and is available even at lower engine speeds. The F8 Spiderâ€™s engine also inherits highly efficient weight-reduction solutions from the 488 Pista which have cut the power unitâ€™s weight by 18 kg compared to that of the 488 Spider.\n\nDESIGN\n\nDesigned by the Ferrari Styling Centre, the F8 Spider continues the direction embarked upon with the F8 Tributo which acted as a bridge to a new design language that will continue to emphasise Ferrariâ€™s key characteristics of high performance and extreme aerodynamic efficiency.\n\nWhen designing a spider, the choice of the top will always play a fundamental role in the carâ€™s overall look. For some years now, Ferrari has been adopting a hard top because of the comfort it provides. As a result, the design of the F8 Spiderâ€™s lines was crafted around its RHT (Retractable Hard Top).\n\nThe key to the whole design was the shifting of the separation line between the carâ€™s body and the roof from its conventional position at the belt-line (occupant shoulder level) to above the B-pillar. The top itself is thus more compact and two-dimensional, with the result that it can be divided into two parts and stowed on top of the engine.\n\nThe RHT takes just 14 seconds to deploy or retract and can be closed or opened while the car is on the move up to 45 km/h.\n\nEXTERIOR\n\nThe goal the Ferrari Styling Centre set with the F8 Spider was to design a stylistic tribute to the Ferrari V8 engine, by evolving the contents of the F8 Tributo and taking inspiration from the most iconic mid-rear-engined V8 sports cars in Ferrari history.\n\nThe result is a car with a strong personality of its own through an even sportier design clearly inspired by the carâ€™s advanced aerodynamics.\n\n\n\nThe front view of the car is characterised by the S-Duct around which the entire front end has been redesigned to highlight the extensive aerodynamic modifications made to this area of the car.\n\nThe clearest example is new, more compact, horizontal LED headlights. The rear spoiler has been entirely redesigned. It is now larger and wraps around the tail lights, visually lowering the carâ€™s centre of gravity and allowing a return to the classic twin light cluster and body-coloured tail, another styling cue from the early 8-cylinder berlinettas like the very first in the legendary series, the 308 GTB.\n\nThe treatment of the engine cover is one of the F8 Spiderâ€™s most distinctive characteristics. The manta-like look of the cover is created by a central spine that starts from the rear screen and disappears under the wing of the blown spoiler, following the air flows themselves.\n\nThe two wings that emerge from the central volume meld harmoniously with the bodywork, lending a sense of visual continuity from all angles. These wing elements are suspended creating an air vent below them which helps improve dissipation of the heat coming off the engine. The three sculpted strakes on the side elements of the engine cover also make their own contribution to this, in addition to referencing the iconic styling of the rear screen of the coupÃ© version.\n\nThe strakes are finished in black to reduce weight low and to lend a sense of visual clarity to the design. The crests that emerge from the prominent volumes of the tonneau cover fins flow sinuously rearwards and into the spoiler in an interpretation of the F1 â€œswan neckâ€\n(the pillars supporting the rear wings) which, in turn, enhances the already-powerfully\nsporty personality of the car.\n\n', 'COCKPIT\n\nThe F8 Spiderâ€™s cockpit retains the classic, driver-oriented look typical of Ferrariâ€™s mid-rear-engined berlinettas. A concept that creates a symbiotic relationship between driver and car, very much as happens in F1, with all controls mounted on the new generation steering wheel. The sporty seats are also new.\n\n\n\n<p>The dash incorporates an aluminium sail panel supporting the central satellite and continuing into the dash itself. Also to create a sense of visual lightness, a sliver of\ncarbon fibre divides the upper and lower parts, streamlining the whole look.\n\n<p>This section also incorporates the optional 7â€ touchscreen passenger-side display and the\ndash is completed by the classic instrument cluster with its central rev-counter.\n\n<p>The tunnel is clearly separated from the dash and set beneath it, once again to enhance the sensation of lightness that the carâ€™s interior exudes. It features a new bridge, a prominent sculptural creation that seems to float and thus further streamlines the cabin.\n\n<p>AERODYNAMICS\n\n<p>The F8 Spider has taken state-of-the-art aerodynamic solutions and innovations from Ferrariâ€™s GT and Challenge racing experience, and moulded them into the production mid-rear-engined drop-top that makes the highest level of performance accessible to drivers of all abilities.\n\n<p>In the F8 Spider, the position of the front radiators â€“ which, unlike the 488 Spider, are\nrearward-angled â€“ is beneficial in cooling terms but simultaneously shrinks the underbody surface area that can be used to generate downforce.\n\n<p>Thus the geometry of the channels used to dissipate hot air had to be redesigned to ensure that maximum downforce was generated whilst cutting drag thanks to the positive\ninteraction between the flows exiting the radiator and the front wheels. The result is a 10% improvement in the carâ€™s overall efficiency compared to the 488 Spider.\n\n<p>VEHICLE DYNAMICS\n\n<p>Overall performance levels are significantly higher than those of the 488 Spider, thanks to the increase in power, weight reduction and improved aerodynamic coefficient.\n\n\n\n<p>That performance is also now accessible to a larger number of drivers thanks to vehicle dynamics systems that make driving on the limit an easier and more confidence-inspiring experience. These include a steering wheel with a smaller-diameter rim and the introduction of the new Ferrari Dynamic Enhancer Plus into the integrated SSC concept, now in 6.1 guise.\n\n<p>To achieve their goal of making the carâ€™s impressive performance easy to access and\ncontrol, Ferrariâ€™s engineers worked on integrating engine and aerodynamics performance with the latest iteration of the vehicle dynamics control systems.\n\n<p>The Side Slip Control system, which improves driversâ€™ control on the limit for an even\nmore engaging behind the wheel, has been further evolved. The transition from version 6.0 to 6.1 reflects the fact that the Ferrari Dynamic Enhancer system (FDE+) now also activates in the Race position of the manettino.\n\n<p>The FDE is a lateral dynamics control system that uses Ferrari software to adjust the brake pressure at the callipers. It debuted on the 488 Pista and was later adopted on the 488 Pista Spider. The F8 Tributo then featured the new FDE+ version with extended functionality which is now also being used on the F8 Spider. The control system, which is operational through and exiting corners (but not under braking), now also extends to low grip conditions and to the Race setting of the manettino.\n\n\n\n<p>7 YEARS MAINTENANCE\n\n<p>Ferrariâ€™s unparalleled quality standards and increasing focus on client service underpin the extended seven-year maintenance programme offered with the F8 Spider. Available across the entire Ferrari range, the programme covers all regular maintenance for the first seven years of the carâ€™s life.\n\n<p>This scheduled maintenance is an exclusive service that allows clients the certainty that their car is being kept at peak performance and safety over the years. This very special service is also available to owners buying pre-owned Ferraris.', '2019-10-22 06:37:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(32, 'two_wheel', 16, 0, 'uploads/3dc3cebe7f2503173fd68ef479ac9884.jpg', 'Gandiva Bikers to Ride 16,000KM to Russia', 8, 'News', 'http://www.astroulagam.com.my', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/8b15054a3d6d6d1e0667d68649f3871b.jpg', 'uploads/6788f69d8f0f4608e3741f70c6866d7b.png', 'undefined', 'HYGcyOHYluI', 'Gandiva Bikers to Ride 16,000KM to Russia', 'The historic feat is Malaysiaâ€™s first ever international bike expedition to Russia and it\'s going to be two Indian bikers; Uthayakumar and Murugan from the Gandiva Motorcycle Club based in Malaysia.\n\nThese bikers are determined to break a record for the â€œLongest Distance Motorcycle Ride by Duoâ€ in the Malaysia Book of Records. Equipped only with their backpacks and Harley Davidsons, Uthayakumar and Murugan will travel across 8 countries, beyond 16,000km for more than 60 days.', 'Starting off this challenging journey at Malaysia Tourism Centre (MaTiC) in Kuala Lumpur on 19 April, the biker duo will ride through Malaysia, Thailand, Cambodia, Vietnam, Laos, China and Mongolia to finally reach Moscow, Russia just in time to watch the first game of the 2018 FIFA World Cup.\n\nDespite riding through the dangerous mountain roads of Kathmandu together a year before, Uthayakumar feels that this â€˜Ride to Russiaâ€™ expedition is going to be FIVE times tougher. Of course, riding a bike with minimal supplies and travelling across the borders is not something everyone is up for.', '2019-10-19 14:27:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(61, 'four_wheel', 13, 0, 'uploads/193886dec8eb5b907900643914e10522.jpg', 'Renault Megane R.S 280 Cup Serba Baharu Terima Suntikan Elemen F1', 1, 'News', 'Editor Oleh Prebiu', '2019-10-09', 'uploads/c30ba0f0309b830396dd940e37a63fd3.jpg', 'uploads/07eabeb1425a12fa656f37bfb8804372.jpg', 'uploads/109679feb9a21f2724da5619d5978cdc.jpg', 'null', 'Renault MEGANE R.S. serba baharu secara rasmi pada harga yang cukup menarik, bersama harga sah untuk transmisi automatik dan di Langkawi\n\n', 'Renault MEGANE R.S. kini rasmi kembali ke pasaran Malaysia dengan gaya yang lebih sporty dan radikal berbanding sebelumnya.\n\n\n\n<p>Diedarkan oleh TC Euro Cars (TCEC), Renault MEGANE R.S. generasi baru kini didatangkan\ndengan transmisi automatik Efficient Dual Clutch (EDC) enam kelajuan, sebagai tambahan kepada transmisi manual (MT) enam kelajuan sedia ada.\n\n<p>Harga untuk Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP dengan kotak gear automatik Efficient Dual Clutch (EDC) sudah ditetapkan. Sementara harga tanpa cukai untuk transmisi manual dan automatik pula telah diturunkan:\n\n<p>Semenanjung Malaysia Bermula Dari RM279,888\nLangkawi Bermula Dari RM149,888\n\n<p>*Semua harga yang dinyatakan adalah di atas jalan termasuk SST, tanpa insurans.\n\n\n\n<p>Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu padat dengan teknologi baru dan yang telah\ndipertingkatkan. Ia terbukti menerusi kesungguhan Renault dalam dunia sukan bermotor demi menawarkan prestasi, pengendalian dan kestabilan luar biasa untuk pemanduan yang lebih selesa dan mengujakan.\n\n<p>Pasukan jurutera memperkenalkan sistem stereng empat roda 4CONTROL â€“ teknologi pertama dalam segmennya di dunia yang meningkatkan lagi kecekapan ketika mengambil selekoh.\n\n<p>Sistem itu berfungsi mengubah suai roda belakang untuk menghala ke arah yang sama dengan roda hadapan sehingga satu darjah pada kelajuan tinggi dan arah bertentangan sehingga 2.7 darjah pada kelajuan lebih rendah. Titik penukaran itu ditetapkan pada kelajuan 60km/j atau 100km/j dalam mode Race.\n\n\n\n<p>Ciri baru yang kedua ialah penambahan empat pemampat hidraulik ke atas penyerap hentak yang diinspirasikan daripada teknologi rali. Bagi menambah baik aspek keselesaan suspensi untuk kegunaan harian, hentian lantunan hidraulik ini juga menghilangkan gangguan apabila dipandu secara lebih sporty.\n\n<p>Pasukan pakar di Renault Sport Cars dan Renault Sport Racing turut mencurahkan segala kepakaran mereka ke atas enjin turbo empat selinder 1.8 liter itu. Mereka telah mereka semula kepala selinder, selain mengintegrasikan satu sistem penyejukan baharu, inlet kemasukan udara berkembar kepada pengecas turbo dan sistem pemasaan yang dipacu oleh rantai.\n\n<p>Hasilnya, enjin yang telah dimodenkan itu mampu menjana kuasa maksimum 280PS dan tork puncak 390Nm â€“ menjadi antara yang terbaik dalam kelasnya. Pecutan 0-100 km/j dapat dilakukan dalam masa 5.8 saat dengan kelajuan maksimum 255km/j (250km/j untuk varian AT).\n\n\n\n<p>Untuk pasaran Malaysia, Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 serba baharu didatangkan dengan chasis CUP. Ia merangkumi mekanikal Torsen dan limited-slip differential untuk menambah baik aspek pengendalian sewaktu pecutan dan memperlahankan kenderaan.\n\n<p>Satu lagi ciri Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP ialah konfiguari lima pintu, berbanding tiga pintu sebelum ini. Pelanggan boleh memilih warna signatur yang baru (Orange Tonic), penambahan kepada warna klasik iaitu kuning (Liquid Yellow).\n\n<p>Kotak gear automatik Efficient Dual Clutch (EDC) untuk keseronokan pemanduan yang tiada tandingan. Kotak gear klac berkembar enam kelajuan EDC telah diperkukuhkan untuk menahan kuasa tork dan rev enjin kereta sports ini.\n\n\n\n<p>Berdasarkan kepada pecutan yang diperlukan, pecutan ketika gear sedang digunakan dan kelajuan maksimum, pasukan jurutera Renault Sport berjaya mendapatkan nisbah gear yang baru dan corak penukaran gear secara spesifik. Ini selari dengan sistem MULTI-SENSE yang boleh diubah suai bagi disesuikan dengan apa jua corak pemanduan.\n\n<p>Sama seperti kereta lumba, kotak gear EDC hadir dengan paddle shifter. Tempoh penukaran gear bergantung kepada mode MULTI-SENSE yang dipilih:\n\n<p>Comfort dan Normal: penukaran gear yang lancar, tanpa sebarang senggukan;\nSport: penukaran gear yang pantas dan bunyi enjin lebih kuat;\nRace: kecekapan tanpa berkompromi dari segi keselesaan, penukaran gear yang lebih\npantas\nDalam mode Sport dan Race, kotak gear EDC juga mempunyai fungsi-fungsi berikut:\n\n<p>Multi-Change Down: ketika membrek dalam mode manual, ciri ini membolehkan pemandu menurunkan beberapa gear secara serta-merta dengan cara menekan dan memegang paddle shifter sebelah kiri. Kedudukan gear yang terbaik kemudian akan dipilih untuk keluar dari selekoh dengan sebaik mungkin.\n\n<p>Launch Control: klac dan turbo telah disediakan lebih awal, membolehkan permulaan pergerakan dilakukan dengan pants seperti sebuah kereta lumba. Dalam mode sport, kawalan cengkaman memberikan sokongan tambahan kepada pemandu untuk mendapatkan cengkaman terbaik dalam kondisi permukaan jalan yang licin.\n\n\n\n<p>Selain daripada teknologi baharu, komponen-komponen utama yang ada pada generasi sebelum ini telah dikekalkan dan ditambah baik pada Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu.\n\n<p>Suspensi hadapan berpaksikan stereng bebas yang dipasang pada MEGANE R.S. sejak tahun 2004 membuktikan kepakaran Renault dalam sistem chasis dan suspensi. Pada asalnya direka untuk kegunaan sukan bermotor, sistem suspensi hadapan berpaksikan stereng bebas telah digunakan pada kenderaan pacuan roda hadapan yang berkuasa tinggi, terutama apabila ia juga dipasang dengan limited-slip differential.\n\n', 'Gandar hadapan Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu telah direka semula sepenuhnya untuk disesuaikan dengan geometri offset negatif rim bersaiz 19 inci dan bagi meningkatkan aspek ketegarannya.\n\n\n\n<p>Cukup dikenali kerana digunakan pada MEGANE R.S. generasi sebelum ini, sistem brek telah ditambah baik. Sekali gus memberi lebih keyakinan kepada pemandu. Diameter cakera brek hadapan telah ditingkatkan kepada 355mm (+15mm berbanding generasi sebelumnya).\n\n<p>Cakera dua material/aluminium/besi tuang membantu mengurangkan berat sehingga 1.8kg bagi setiap roda. Pada masa yang sama menambah baik aspek penyejukan ketika digunakan secara intensif.\n\n<p>Tetapan pedal brek memberi fokus kepada ketepatan tekanan yang dikenakan. Ini membolehkan pemandu dapat mengawal kenderaan sepenuhnya, terutama di litar lumba. R.S. Monitor juga telah disemak semula sepenuhnya dengan susun atur lebih mesra pengguna dan ciri yang lebih berkuasa.\n\n\n\n<p>Sistem telemetri dan pemerolehan data yang canggih ini berfungsi mengumpul serta merumuskan maklumat daripada lebih 40 unit sensor yang dipasang pada seluruh kenderaan. Ia membolehkan pelbagai talaan kereta dipaparkan pada masa sebenar menerusi tablet dengan skrin sentuh R-LINK 2 bersaiz 8.7 inci.\n\n<p>Melalui sistem ini, pemandu boleh memeriksa pelbagai data pemanduan seperti pecutan, brek, yaw, sudut stereng, operasi sistem 4CONTROL suhu dan tekanan.\n\n<p>Apabila reka bentuk juga bermaksud prestasi Dengan gayaannya yang ekspresif dan sporty, Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu telah direka untuk menawarkan prestasi, sehinggalah ke perincian yang terakhir.\n\n\n\n<p>Rekaan sisi badan yang spesifik membolehkan wing dilebarkan sebanyak 60mm di bahagian belakang dan 45mm di belakang. Jentera ini juga telah direndahkan sebanyak 5mm, dengan rim baharu bersaiz 19 inci, perkadaran baru itu membuatkan penampilan kereta nampak lebih agresif.\n\n<p>Reka bentuk penuh kuasa itu ditingkatkan lagi dengan sejumlah ciri yang diambil daripada dunia sukan bermotor. Sekali gus meletakkan Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu dalam kategori jentera berprestasi tinggi:\n\n<p>Corong pengambilan udara yang lebar pada bampar hadapan bersama bilah seperti jentera F1, merupakan gayaan signatur Renault Sport yang menjadi refleksi kepada pembabitan jenama ini dalam Formula 1.\nBilah-bilah yang menerima kemasan warna kelabu satin (Gun Metal Grey) kontras dengan bahagian lain yang lebih berkilat.\nRekaan corak sarang lebah secara 3D pada gril mengukuhkan lagi DNA Renault Sport\nBahagian sisi kenderaan yang maskulin diwarisi daripada reka bentuk Renault MEGANE\nyang disempurnakan lagi dengan trak hadapan dan belakang yang lebih lebar\nPengekstrak udara pada bahagian sisi mengoptimumkan aliran udara pada arca roda\nSil sisi mengukuhkan lagi hubungan di antara bahagian hadapan dan belakang, bilah\nberwarna hitam itu pula menyerlahkan gayaan sebuah jentera Formula 1\nSpoiler belakang yang lebih nipis itu telah direka semua untuk menambah baik prestasi\naerodinamik. Selain membuatkan kereta kelihatan lebih lebar, corong vertikal itu\nmeningkatkan aspek aerodinamik dengan menambah baik aliran udara\nBampar belakang dengan peresap udara binaan dalam dan ekzos diletakkan di bahagian\ntengah menyerlahkan lagi gayaan MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP\nKecekapan peresap udara ditingkatkan berbanding generasi terdahulu. Selain\nmembuatkan rekaan lebih sporty, komponen aerodinamik itu membantu meningkatkan\nkuasa downforce.\nAngkup brek Brembo diberi warna merah pada chasis Cup, jadi ia lebih mudah dikenali\noleh para peminatnya.\nLampu R.S. Vision berprestasi tinggi yang unik dalam segmen ini menggabungkan empat fungsi: lampu sisi, lampu membelok, lampu kabus dan lampu tinggi jarak jauh\n\n<p>Nico Hulkenberg with the All-New Renault MEGANE R.S.\nKebolehdapatan dan pandu uji\n\n<p>Renault MEGANE R.S. 280 CUP serba baharu boleh didapati dalam empat pilihan warna â€“ hitam (Diamond Black), putih mutiara (Pearl White) (tambah RM1,000) dan warna signatur kuning (Liquid Yellow) atau oren (Orange Tonic) (tambah RM8,000).\n\n<p>Pandu uji boleh dilakukan di beberapa bilik pameran terpilih Renault melalui temu janji sahaja dan boleh dipohon melalui laman web Renault Malaysia.', '2019-10-22 07:02:25', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(34, 'four_wheel', 14, 0, 'uploads/98d3abff756a5d183335e681d08ca78e.jpg', 'Saga 2019 Lebih Bergaya Dan Pintar', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/bb066cdff436fa9a83fc343ab5bc715f.jpg', 'uploads/5e829b0bf2d9af4d47dced0e2f9766a6.jpg', 'uploads/18556e250b783a5bb2a98719539ad1e7.jpg', 'null', 'Penggayaan baharu, sistem infotainmen skrin sesentuh dan transmisi auto 4-kelajuan\n\nPROTON melancarkan Saga 2019 di Pusat Pameran dan Perdagangan Antarabangsa Malaysia (MITEC) dan dirasmikan oleh Menteri Perdagangan Antarabangsa dan Industri, Datoâ€™ Darell Leiking.', 'Turut hadir ialah Datoâ€™ Mohammad Zainal Shaari, Pengerusi DRB-Hicom, Datoâ€™ Sri Syed Faisal Albar, Pengerusi Proton, Dr. Li Chunrong, Ketua Pegawai Eksekutif Proton serta Datoâ€™ Radzaif Mohamed, Timbalan Ketua Pegawai Eksekutif Proton.\n\n<p>Harga bermula RM32,800 (Standard MT), RM35,800 (Standard AT) dan RM39,800 (Premium AT), versi terbaharu model ikonik dan terlaris ini dilengkapi dengan gaya baharu, kotak gear automatik empat kelajuan dan ciri pintar pertama di dalam kelasnya yang bukan sahaja membezakannya daripada pesaing tetapi turut meningkatkan nilainya.\n\n<p>Syarikat juga mengenal pasti proposisi penjualan unik atau Unique Selling Propositions (USP) model ini iaitu apabila digabungkan, menghasilkan slogan Pilihan Yang Pintar atau An Intelligent Proposition. Tiga USP yang dinyatakan adalah Gaya Mengujakan, Penjimatan Bijak dan Kestabilan Mantap.\n\n<p>Kisah mengenai Proton Saga adalah sinonim dengan Proton, mengimbau kembali 34 tahun lalu dan tiga perubahan sepenuhnya dilakukan pada model tersebut.\n\n<p>Saga 2019 telah diberikan rekaan terkini yang masih mengekalkan identitinya tetapi pada masa yang sama meletakkannya ke barisan model Proton yang lain.\n\n<p>Rekaan Luaran\n\n\n\n \n\n<p>Saga 2019 dipasangkan dengan bampar hadapan baharu dan lebih agresif bersepadu dengan lampu nyalaan siang. Pada bahagian gril turut mempunyai corak infinite weave yang mula diperkenalkan melalui model Proton X70 serta Iriz dan Persona 2019.\n\n<p>Bampar belakang yang sama menonjol sepadan dengan bahagian hadapan dan rekaan di belakang dilengkapi dengan spoiler belakang bersepadu baharu dan nama Proton terletak pada bahagian penutup but.\n\n<p>Set roda aloi bersaiz 15 inci yang menampilkan rekaan baharu menyerikan lagi sentuhan akhir pada varian premium.\n\n<p>Dalaman\n\n\n\n<p>Pada bahagian dalam pula, perubahan paling ketara dilakukan adalah pada monitor skrin sesentuh 7-inci terapung atau floating touchscreen pada model premium.\n\n \n\n<p>Digunakan untuk mengawal sistem infotainmen, kemudahan ini mempunyai sambungan Bluetooth, kapasiti penyimpanan dalaman 16GB dan sambungan telefon pintar untuk Android.\n\n<p>Perubahan lain termasuklah upholsteri tempat duduk baharu, panel tengah baharu, paparan kombinasi meter baharu dengan Bantuan Pemanduan Eco dan turut dilengkapi sehingga 3 tempat cucuk USB.\n\n<p>Kemudahan yang turut disediakan dalam Saga 2019 ini termasuklah kunci pembuka but, pelindung matahari dengan pemegang kad dan cermin, lampu peta LED dan pemegang genggaman baharu untuk disepadankan dengan bahan yang digunakan di bahagian dalaman kereta.\n\n\n\nSecara mekanikal, perubahan paling besar adalah transmisi automatik empat kelajuan baharu menggantikan CVT yang digunakan sebelum ini.\n\nBarisan Jurutera Proton kemudiannya membuat peningkatan pada prestasi brek, tahap kebisingan, getaran dan kekasaran (NVH) serta keseimbangan pemanduan dan pengendalian disamping menambah tahap keselamatan yang berkelas dunia.\n\nSebagai contoh brek yang dilengkapkan pada model ini adalah sama seperti yang dipasangkan pada Proton Iriz dan Persona yang lebih besar manakala penggunaan kotak gear automatik empat kelajuan baharu memberikan pemandu kawalan manual yang lebih baik semasa memandu dengan penuh tenaga.\n\n', 'Ciri Keselamatan\n\n<p>Ciri-ciri keselamatan pada model ini terdiri daripada Brek Anti Kekunci (ABS) dengan Agihan Brek Elektronik (EBD) dan Bantuan Brek (BA) untuk ketiga-tiga varian yang turut dilengkapi dengan beg udara depan, sensor tempat letak kereta belakang dan titik penahan ISOFIX dengan top tethers.\n\n<p>Tambahan pada varian Premium adalah Bantuan Kawalan Cerun, sensor tempat letak kereta hadapan, kamera undur dan Kawalan Kestabilan Elektronik (ESC) dengan Sistem Kawalan Cengkaman (TCS).\n\n<p>Dengan pertambahan ciri-ciri keselamatan ini, Saga 2019 menjadi satu-satunya kereta yang berharga kurang daripada RM40,000 dilengkapi ESC dan TCS.\n\n\n\n<p>Sama seperti Proton X70, Iriz, Persona dan Exora 2019, Saga baharu ini menawarkan pakej Nilai Tambahan atau Extra Value. Terdapat tiga pakej Nilai Tambahan standard yang bermula dengan pakej servis yang menawarkan kos pekerja percuma sebanyak tiga kali atau selama satu tahun.\n\n<p>Seterusnya adalah pakej kadar faedah dengan kadar pembiayaan serendah 2.98% setahun. Akhir sekali ialah pakej insurans yang menawarkan pelbagai manfaat kepada pelanggan yang menginsuranskan pembelian baharu mereka dengan panel Proton.\n\n<p>Digabungkan dengan pengurangan harga dan nilai ciri-ciri baharu yang diperkenalkan dalam setiap varian, Saga 2019 Premium AT 1.3L memberi nilai tambahan sebanyak RM3,747 berbanding model sebelum ini.\n\n<p>Bagi varian Standard AT 1.3L pula memberi penjimatan sebanyak RM2,043 manakala Standard MT 1.3L mempunyai nilai tambahan sebanyak RM2,291 untuk mereka yang membelinya.', '2019-10-22 06:38:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(35, 'four_wheel', 14, 0, 'uploads/c11d0cbc3563036a973236e8f1fbb17a.jpg', 'Perodua Myvi Generasi Ketiga Dilancar Di Mauritius', 1, 'News', 'Prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/a002e85eaf65499d087d55af6e5086e0.jpg', 'uploads/596df3bd9679b0f6a0cef010bbe98c6d.jpg', 'uploads/8a23022e313c00045f216076d4f01e34.jpg', 'null', 'Perodua telah melancarkan Perodua Myvi generasi ketiga di Mauritius yang ditawarkan dalam varian 1.3 G AT dan 1.5 H AT, dengan harga masing-masing 699,000 (RM81,300*) dan 775,000 (RM90,140*) Rupee Mauritius, atas jalan termasuk insurans.\n\n', 'PENGEDAR tempatan, Raouf Dusmohamud & Co Ltd, telah mempamerkan Perodua Myvi di Defi Media Motor Show yang berlangsung di Swami Vivekananda International Conference Centre pada hujung minggu yang lalu.\n\n\n\n<p>â€œPerodua Myvi generasi ketiga ini telah diterima baik di Malaysia dan kami percaya rakyat Mauritius akan tertarik kepada ciri-ciri yang terdapat pada model ini,â€ kata Presiden dan Ketua Pegawai Eksekutif Perodua Datoâ€™ Zainal Abidin Ahmad.\n\n<p>â€œPerodua berhasrat untuk mengeksport 3,270 kenderaan pada 2019 â€“ peningkatan sebanyak 50% berbanding 2,184 unit tahun lepas. Setakat tahun ini, kami telah menjual lebih 1,600 unit di luar Malaysia dan melancarkan Myvi dan Axia masing-masing di Singapura dan Seychelles.\n\n<p>â€œPenampilan sulung Myvi di Mauritius akan mendekatkan kami kepada sasaran eksport akhir-tahun kami dan secara tidak langsung meningkatkan jenama Perodua di peringkat antarabangsa, memandangkan Mauritius terkenal sebagai destinasi pelancongan yang popular,â€ katanya.\n\n<p>Perodua Myvi mempunyai kecekapan bahan api melebihi 20 km/l dan memegang penarafan keselamatan penuh ASEAN NCAP lima bintang. Gaya yang unik, ruang dalaman yang menakjubkan serta ciri-ciri pintar dan praktikal digabungkan dengan kualiti tinggi untuk memberikan keselesaan dan kemudahan kepada pemandu serta penumpang.\n\n\n\n<p>â€œDilengkapi dengan lampu LED, sistem kemasukan dan penghidup enjin tanpa kunci, Bluetooth, empat atau enam beg udara, serta kawalan kestabilan yang terdapat pada kedua-dua varian, Myvi baharu merupakan kenderaan canggih yang dinanti-nantikan oleh rakyat Mauritius,â€ kata Pengarah Urusan Raouf Dusmohamud & Co Ltd, Raouf Dusmohamud.\n\n<p>â€œKami menawarkan servis percuma sehingga 30,000 km bagi Myvi, dan kini kami juga memanjangkan tawaran yang sama kepada setiap pembelian model-model Perodua kami yang lain, iaitu Alza, Axia dan Bezza,â€ katanya.\n\n', 'Mauritius adalah pasaran eksport ketiga bagi Myvi generasi ketiga selepas Indonesia (di mana ia dijual sebagai Daihatsu Sirion) dan Singapura.\n\n<p>Negara kepulauan yang terletak di Lautan Hindi itu merupakan antara pasaran luar negara Perodua yang paling lama. Hampir 2,400 kenderaan Perodua telah dijual di sana sejak 1996, termasuk Kancil, Rusa, Kembara, Kenari, Kelisa, Myvi generasi pertama dan kedua, Viva dan kini Alza, Axia dan Bezza.', '2019-10-22 06:39:49', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(36, 'two_wheel', 1, 0, 'uploads/25c33465b2231aa467aae14d95603242.jpg', 'New Colours for 2019 Yamaha Ego Avantiz', 8, 'News', ' Wahid Ooi Abdullah', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/549cfed5cf215de846ee3cc1895600a1.jpg', 'uploads/5f2a1e4ec6261895d9a799085a259252.jpg', 'uploads/411f5df90eb18b5f579f7bcf723cb187.jpg', 'null', 'New Colours for 2019 Yamaha Ego Avantiz\nThere are four new colours for the 2019 Yamaha Ego Avantiz.\n', 'There are four new colours for the 2019 Yamaha Ego Avantiz.\nThe model has been sold since 2016.\nIt continues to be popular among Malaysia motorcyclists.\nMention the name â€œYamahaâ€ in the small motorcycle segment and the Ysuku (Y15ZR) is the first model that comes to mind. Truth is, other models sell just as well. Thatâ€™s why Hong Leong Yamaha Motor (HLYM) has just rolled out new colours for the 2019 Yamaha Ego Altiz.\n\n<p>Launched in 2016, the Ego Avantiz is the most popular twist-and-go scooter in its segment despite the onslaught of competitors.\nThe Yamaha is powered by a 125cc, air-cooled, SOHC engine which utilises Yamahaâ€™s Blue Core set of solutions for optimum operational. The criteria include efficiency in cooling, low friction and lubrication. Consequently, the engine produces more power and torque while minimising fuel consumption and emissions.\n\n<p>Yamaha scooters always feature lots of storage space and the Ego Avantiz has a 14-litre underseat storage capacity.\nAdditionally, this model pioneered the use of LED headlamps and taillamp in its segment.\n\n', 'More importantly, the bike has a low seat height, making it accessible to anyone. But most important of all is its very affordable price.\nSo, itâ€™s easy to see why the bike is still popular among Malaysian motorcyclists. As such, HLYM introduced four new colours for the 2019 Yamaha Ego Avantiz.\n\n<p>They are Blue, Cyan, Grey and Red. Pricing remains unchanged at RM 5,536 (basic sales price and not on-the-road). They will be available from this month onwards.', '2019-10-19 14:22:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(37, 'four_wheel', 12, 0, 'uploads/39d0b046c1c8841d9f741569e10b37bf.jpg', 'VW Arteon Serba Baharu ', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/320ec13e913062fc1f6108b9ae5556fa.jpg', 'uploads/585e7f0a26f4d970824fff85664adb45.jpg', 'uploads/2f3a99a67db3448f877242bbe4dd63c7.jpg', 'null', 'VW Arteon Serba Baharu  Kini Dibuka Untuk Tempahan â€“ Harga Bermula RM290k Hingga RM310k', 'Volkswagen Passenger Cars Malaysia (VPCM) kini mula menerima pra-tempahan untuk Volkswagen Arteon serba baharu.\n\n<p>VOLKSWAGEN Arteon R-Line yang diimport sepenuhnya itu dijangka ditawarkan pada harga di antara RM290,000 dan RM310,000 apabila dilancarkan dalam tempoh beberapa bulan lagi.\n\n\n\n<p>Menampilkan rekaan yang mengagumkan apabila dilihat daripada semua sudut, fastback 5-pintu itu merupakan model utama Volkswagen dan menawarkan reka bentuk avant-garde bersama pengendalian dinamik.\n\n<p>Namanya menjadi refleksi sebenar penampilannya â€“ â€˜Artâ€™ menerangkan tentang garis-garis badan sebuah fastback yang harmoni dan beremosi manakala â€˜eonâ€™ pula menyerlahkannya sebagai sebuah model premium Volkswagen.\n\n<p>Arteon telah dipilih sebagai pemenang â€œ2017 Golden Steering Wheelâ€, salah satu anugerah automotif paling berprestij di Eropah.\n\n\n\n', 'Dibina untuk kelajuan, Arteon dikuasakan oleh enjin turbo a 2.0L TSI yang dipadankan bersama kotak gear basah direct shift gearbox (DSG) 7-kelajuan. Kuasa mencecah 280PS dan tork 350Nm yang boleh dicapai di antara 5,100 hingga 6,500rpm itu disalurkan ke roda menerusi sistem pacuan semua roda 4MOTION.\n\n<p>Dilengkapi Paparan Info Aktif dengan paparan transistor warna filem nipis (TFT), tetapan baru membolehkan ubah suai dan paparan peta sepenuhnya dibuat.\n\n<p>Sistem infohibur Discover Pro baharu yang terdiri daripada skrin bersaiz 9.2 inci pula hadir dengan ciri kawalan gestur dan Ketersambungan Aplikasi tanpa Wayar (CarPlay, Android Auto dan MirrorLink).\n\n<p>Untuk memberi lebih kemudahan, kamera 360-darjah yang baru membolehkan pemandu melihat kawasan di sekeliling kenderaan menerusi empat unit kamera bersepadu.\n\n\n\n<p>Arteon hadir dengan pakej gayaan dalaman dan luaran R-Line. Ia didatangkan dalam lapan warna â€“ kelabu (Manganese Grey), hitam (Deep Black), perak (Reflex Silver), merah (Romance Red), kelabu (Urano Grey), kuning (Turmeric Yellow), putih mutiara (Oryx White Pearl) dan perak (Pyrite Silver).\n\n<p>Arteon serba baharu akan membuat penampilan awal di bilik-bilik pameran Volkswagen. Orang ramai yang ingin melihatnya secara dekat dijemput untuk mendaftarkan minat mereka di laman web Volkswagen bagi menerima jemputan eksklusif.', '2019-10-22 06:41:32', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(38, 'two_wheel', 16, 0, 'uploads/636031a06b26ea469b77258ef0d66edc.jpg', 'BMW Motorrad Malaysia Introduces Engine Oil Inclusive, Service Inclusive and Warranty Extension Programmes', 8, 'News', 'Wahid Ooi Abdullah', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/42fc3d8ddbbd42c4b041aeb634c5d10c.jpg', 'undefined', 'undefined', 'null', 'BMW Motorrad Malaysia Introduces Engine Oil Inclusive, Service Inclusive and Warranty Extension Programmes', 'BMW Motorrad Malaysia rolled out exclusive aftersales programmes.\nThey are called Engine Oil Inclusive, Service Inclusive and Warranty Extension.\nThey offer BMW owners a complete peace of mind.\nBMW Motorrad Malaysia introduced three new aftersales care programmes called Engine Oil Inclusive, Service Inclusive and Warranty Extension. The programmes cover new and existing BMW motorcycle customers in Malaysia.\n\n<p>BMW Motorrad Engine Oil Inclusive\nThis first ever Engine Oil Inclusive programme has two options i.e. three years (or 30,000KM) or five years (or 50,000KM). The programme offers regular engine oil services which also includes BMW ADVANTEC genuine oil and filter replacement for all new and registered BMW motorcycles dated under 10 years from first registration. The maintenance history of the motorcycles should be in accordance to the recommended service intervals and performed at authorised BMW Motorrad dealerships in the country for the programme to be valid.\n\n<p>BMW Motorrad Service Inclusive\nThe BMW Motorrad Service Inclusive programme offers an additional PLUS over and above the BMW Motorrad Engine Oil Inclusive programme. With Service Inclusive, customers are covered in terms of Valve Clearance Check, Fork Oil Check, Transmission Oil Change, Spark Plug replacement, Brake Fluid Change, Air Filter Change, CVT Belt Replacement, Fuel Filter Change and Rear Axle Oil Change. \n\n<p>Programme options are also over a period of three years (or 30,000KM) or five years (or 50,000KM), and is also available for BMW motorcycles under 10 years from its date of first registration. Prior maintenance history of the motorcycle should also be in accordance to the recommended service intervals and performed at authorised BMW Motorrad dealerships.', 'BMW Motorrad Warranty Extension \nThe BMW Motorrad Warranty Extension programme offers an added extension of the manufacturerâ€™s warranty after the expiration of the statutory warranty period, including corrective work repairs with BMW genuine parts. \n\nThe add-on programme can be purchased as an additional one-year or two-year package above and beyond the manufacturerâ€™s warranty, which was raised to a standard of three years for BMW motorcycles registered from January 1st, 2019.\n\nThe programme is available on offer for new and registered motorcycles dated 90 days from its first registration, but excludes the BMW Motorrad offering of the Roadside Assistance programme introduced earlier this year.\n\nHarald Hoelzl, Managing Director of BMW Group Malaysia said, â€œA complete peace of mind ownership experience is the key to premium expression of a vehicle from the BMW Group. It is also how we differentiate ourselves to create value for our customers in the premium automotive industry.â€\n\nHoelzl added that the ownership experience beyond the purchase of the vehicle is as important as the moment of truth in the purchasing decision process. He said, â€œThis is the very reason we have the best ownership experience in the industry, from the best service and warranty programme to the best customer experience programme which can be seen in our monthly Net Promoter Scores (NPS).â€\n\nOwen Riley, Head of BMW Motorrad Malaysia said, â€œThe new programmes are firsts in the Premium Motorcycle industry here in Malaysia.  They are backed by the same standards we have for BMW Motorrad worldwide and are on offer at all our authorised BMW Motorrad dealerships. The aim here is to look after our customers in all the areas of maintenance so that they can simply Make Life a Ride!â€ \n\nRecommended Retail Pricing for the First-Ever Service and Warranty Extension programmes are as per the attached price list. All programmes are also eligible to be financed completely from BMW Group Financial Services Malaysia.\n\nFor more information on the First-Ever Service and Warranty Programmes from BMW Motorrad Malaysia please visit <a href=\"https://www.bmwmotorrad.com.my/en/service/services/warranty.html\" target=\"_blank\"> https://www.bmwmotorrad.com.my/ en/service/services/warranty.html.</a>', '2019-10-19 14:16:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(60, 'four_wheel', 13, 0, 'uploads/1d0f78455fa07c7909e01b090d0d7700.jpg', 'Nasim Launches New Peugeot 3008 SUV Plus And 5008 SUV Plus', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu', '2019-10-09', 'uploads/e8b2fed25a2b6713990890eea794b665.jpg', 'uploads/5086d2bbbb15e3595dc14cf747390ab0.jpg', 'uploads/9c555df1fd3fc9e5325ec38a1af4be9d.jpg', 'null', 'Nasim Sdn Bhd, the official distributor for the Peugeot brand in Malaysia, has kicked into high gear for second half of 2019 through the launch of the New Peugeot 3008 SUV Plus and New Peugeot 5008 SUV Plus.\n\n', 'SM Nasarudin SM Nasimuddin, Group Executive Chairman & CEO, Naza Corporation Holdings said, â€œThe New Peugeot 3008 SUV Plus and New Peugeot 5008 SUV Plus are the culmination of a joint agreement in 2018 between Naza Group and Groupe PSA to establish Naza Automotive Manufacturing (NAM) as the Southeast Asia hub.\n\n\n\n<p>We are excited to be celebrating this milestone with two of Peugeotâ€™s best performing models that continue to blaze the trail for SUVs and pushing boundaries of possibility.â€\n\n<p>â€œNAM has benefited greatly from progressive enhancements since Groupe PSAâ€™s involvement, including expertise from a dedicated industrial team and technology transfer from the latterâ€™s headquarters in France.\n\n<p>We are excited to unveil another two SUVs produced by NAM for local distribution and regional export in the near future,â€ added SM Nasarudin.\n\n<p>Continuing their momentum into second half of 2019, Nasim is confident of a strong sales performance this year driven by demands for its SUVs.\n\n\n\n<p>The New Peugeot 3008 SUV Plus underscores the French marqueâ€™s expertise in crafting a highly successful SUV that is built on the principles of design and advanced technology. The global success for the winner of â€˜European Car Of The Year 2017â€™ and â€˜Malaysia Automotive Instituteâ€™s Car Of The Year 2018â€™ evidently resonated with Malaysian road users last year by recording the countryâ€™s highest sales volume for a European SUV.\n\n<p>Just as equally impressive is the New Peugeot 5008 SUV Plus whose predecessor successfully entered the C-segment SUV territory as an expressive 7-seater that assimilates the space and practicality of an MPV with the dynamic appeal of an SUV.\n\n<p>Now improved with upgraded creature comforts and technology, the SUV has trumped over established competition to clinch the 7-Seater SUV of the Year at the DSF.my VOTY Awards 2019 and Best Family SUV at the Cars of Malaysia 2019.\n\n\n\n<p>While its distinctive front face retains a floating grille design and LED Sequential Scrolling Indicator, the vehicle dons a new roof rail design and chrome side mirrors reaffirming the vehicleâ€™s muscular yet elegant characteristics.\n\n<p>Both the New 3008 SUV Plus and New 5008 SUV Plus come with a new panoramic sunroof and sport 18-inch alloy wheels in two-tone diamond finish.\n\n<p>The sophisticated interior is an invitation to experience comfort, serenity and luxury. Once inside, occupants are welcomed by plush Claudia leather seats with either Graphite or Goa stitching that varies by the variant. Maintaining its fresh and dignified leather and fabric dashboard and door panel dÃ©cor, the dashboard is further illuminated by blue mood lighting touches all around the cabin.\n\n<p>Committed to delivering a high-end experience, the new Peugeot i-Cockpit reflects this promise through numerous thoughtful touches. A new Navigation function is now embedded in the 8-inch Multifunction Colour touchscreen on both the New 3008 SUV Plus and New 5008 SUV Plus.\n\n\n\nThe segment-leading 12.3-inch high-resolution Head-Up Digital Cluster Display becomes more customisable with the addition of â€˜Onyxâ€™ graphical style, a new â€˜Driving Assistanceâ€™ display mode and new tailor-made â€˜Personalâ€™ modes. The New 5008 SUV Plus can display an additional â€˜Navigationâ€™ mode to reflect map manoeuvres right in the driverâ€™s eye level.\n\nPeugeot i-Cockpit Amplify adds a touch of youthfulness to the cabin by allowing the adaptation of key settings enabled by two distinctive ambiances that evoke emotional satisfaction: â€˜BOOSTâ€™ for a dynamic experience or â€˜RELAXâ€™ to envelope the occupants in a serene ambiance.\n\nActivating the new Drive Sport Pack heightens the sight, touch and hearing senses for a sporty grip and feeling through stiffer assisted steering, more responsive accelerator, greater engine and gearbox agility and digitally amplified engine sound.\n\n', '\n\nAn ingenious motorised smart tailgate is built into both models to provide convenience in opening and closing the boot hands-free with a swift foot motion under the bumperâ€™s centre.\n\n<p>To fully appreciate the capability of the New 3008 SUV Plus and New 5008 SUV Plus takes a multitude of Advanced Driver Assistance Systems such as Driver Attention Alert, Speed Limit Recognition and Recommendation, 180 degree reverse camera with stitching function, and an upgraded Blind Spot Information System and Active Lane Departure Warning, which utilises a windscreen camera to detect road markings and automatically adjusts the vehicleâ€™s direction slightly while alerting the driver.\n\n<p>Reinforcing safety are industry standard features such as 6 safety airbags, Advanced Electronic Stability Program, Advanced Grip Control, Hill Start Assist, Indirect Tyre Pressure Detection and an Electronic Stability Program which incorporates Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD), Emergency Brake Assistance (EBA), Wheel Anti-Slip Regulation (ASR) and Dynamic Stability Control (DSC).\n\n\n\n<p>The Active base variant of the New Peugeot 3008 SUV Plus is offered at RM150,888 while the higher spec Allure variant goes for RM163,888, both on-the-road prices excluding insurance. The New Peugeot 5008 SUV Plus also comes in the Active and Allure variants, priced at RM166,888 and RM179,888 respectively.\n\n<p>Both models and their variants come in Nera Black, Pearl White, Amazonite Grey and the new Aster Grey colours, with the New 3008 SUV Plus receiving an exclusive Metallic Copper colour and the New 5008 SUV Plus getting the distinctive Emerald Crystal finish.\n\n<p>In line with Peugeotâ€™s distinguished standards and to provide the best ownership experience, both SUVs come with 5 Years Peace of Mind warranty, 3 Years Free Service, together with Nasimâ€™s existing 24-hours Peugeot Assistance towing service and complimentary access to SkyLounge by Naza at Subang Skypark*.', '2019-10-22 07:03:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0);
