(40, 'two_wheel', 6, 0, 'uploads/920445ac1a3257587cfca19205dd277b.jpg', 'Yamaha YZF-R15 Monster Energy GP Edition Coming to Malaysia â€“ From RM12,618', 8, 'News', ' Wahid Ooi Abdullah', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/3266c7087fee25b7f368cbf3779f31d9.jpg', 'undefined', 'uploads/7cec096e65f0debea57bd88c4530beb0.jpg', 'null', 'Yamaha YZF-R15 Monster Energy GP Edition Coming to Malaysia â€“ From RM12,618', 'The Yamaha YZF-R15 Monster Energy GP Edition is coming to Malaysia.\nIts livery is exactly as the Yamaha MotoGP works bikeâ€™s.\nThe recommended basic selling price is from RM12,618.\nThe Yamaha YZF-R15 Monster Energy GP Edition is headed to Malaysia. The livery is derived directly from the Monster Energy Yamaha MotoGP works team.\n\n<p>Yamaha has always transferred their MotoGP liveries to their motorcycles in many markets including Malaysia. That started long ago with the 135 LC, then the Y15ZR, YZF-R25 and now the YZF-R15 (R15).\n', 'The Monster Energy GP edition was launched in the UK on the YZF-R125 months ago and it was high time for our turn.\nWhat makes it special this time is the Monster Energy livery which was replicated by enthusiasts on their own. It was said that the Monster Energy sponsorship in MotoGP was brought along by Valentino Rossi. The energy drink sponsored him since the Movistar days.\nThe bike is mechanically identical to the standard R15. We found the standard bike good enough already anyway, so thereâ€™s no sense in disturbing its equilibrium.\n\n<p>However, to those whoâ€™ve not ridden the R15, the upside-down forks, chassis and 155cc VVT engine produce a lively and entertaining ride. You could even knee down in corners if ridden well.\nThe recommended basic selling price is from RM12,618 (not including road tax, insurance and number plates).', '2019-10-19 14:21:27', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(41, 'four_wheel', 13, 0, 'uploads/2aa3dbaca3a05d849b64b2928aaed911.jpg', 'Memperkenalkan BMW X7 â€“ Cukup Futuristik Pada Harga RM888,800', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/cf11050f32a61d0c44b5ca28cca75ace.jpg', 'uploads/c460f4d2d366996f06b724cd4583d5d8.jpg', 'uploads/4c4c2130ca870ae0f4745edb2bb71dbd.jpg', 'null', 'BMW Malaysia memperkenalkan BMW X7 yang pertama, ikon terkini yang melambangkan definisi kemewahan progresif yang baharu.\n\n', 'KENDERAAN Sport Aktiviti (SAV) milik BMW dalam segmen kenderaan mewah ini mencerminkan kualiti yang bertaraf tertinggi dalam aspek kemodenan, kemewahan dan pesona, serta ia memahat tanda aras baharu dalam segmen tersebut.\n\n\n\n<p>Sashi Ambi, Ketua Komunikasi Korporat BMW Group Malaysia berkata, â€œDimensi kemodenan dan kemewahan progresif telah menjadi daya peneraju dalam penawaran produk global yang terbesar daripada BMW Group, dan BMW X7 mendemonstrasikan prinsip yang kami guna pakai untuk segmen automotif mewah.\n\n<p>â€œModel-model BMW X dikategorikan sebagai model yang tersohor dalam portfolio BMW dan ia berjaya mencatat penyerahan berjumlah lebih daripada lima juta unit di persada antarabangsa sejak ia diperkenalkan.\n\n<p>Di Malaysia, kenderaan BMW X melakar penyerahan yang berjumlah lebih daripada 5,000 unit di seluruh negara pada tahun 2018.\n\n<p>Jentera SAV mewah ini memperlihatkan bagaimana ambien eksklusif model BMW X dibawa ke sedan BMW 7 Series buat julung kali, ia mendemonstrasikan strategi pengeluar kenderaan premium ini yang seterusnya dalam segmen kenderaan mewah.\n\n\n\n<p>Model kenderaan dalam famili BMW X yang terbaharu dan yang terbesar ini menampilkan teknologi â€˜powertrainâ€™ dan casis yang mengagumkan, selain daripada ruang kabin yang luas di setiap tiga seksyen barisan tempat duduknya, ambien yang serba mewah serta ciri-ciri kelengkapan yang canggih turut membawakan sebuah pengalaman pemanduan yang tiada tandingannya.\n\n<p>Rekabentuk luaran\n\n<p>Bahagian luaran BMW X7 ini hadir dengan reka bentuk megah dan rapi. Seksyen hadapan yang lebih besar bersama gril â€˜kidneyâ€™ yang ikonik menonjolkan kehadiran jentera ini di atas jalan raya, berserta dengan â€˜BMW Laserlightâ€™ bersaiz langsing yang mampu mencahayakan laluan di hadapan sejauh 600 meter, dan pada masa sama kontras dapat dilihat dengan jelas.\n\n<p>Ditawarkan sebagai standard, lampu kabus LED serta sistem bantuan lampu puncak juga melengkapi BMW X7. Bahagian bawah apron yang terletak di muncung kenderaan ini memiliki elemen trim yang mengunjur merentasi kelebaran jentera tersebut dan ia membingkaikan komponen salur masuk udara.\n\n<p>Dari sisi, garisan bahu yang hampir vertikal sepenuhnya membuahkan penampilan yang memanjang dari seksyen hadapan ke belakang. Seperti BMW 7 Series, ia didatangkan dengan liang udara, â€˜Air Breatherâ€™ yang lain daripada yang lain dalam elemen krom.\n\n\n\n<p>Tingkap yang lebih besar serta garis bumbung yang lebih memanjang menerusi kaedah yang dinamik memperlihatkan keluasan interior jentera alaf baharu ini. Pintu belakang berukuran lebih panjang berbanding pintu hadapan, ia menekankan keluasan kompartmen belakang yang memudahkan penumpang untuk masuk dan keluar dari jentera ini.\n\n<p>Tidak kurang menariknya, set roda aloi ringan 21 inci dalam penggayaan Y-spoke dwiwarna 753 dengan tayar â€˜run-flatâ€™ juga ditawarkan sebagai standard.\n\n<p>Dengan jarak kelegaan tanah (ground clearance) dan bahagian belakang yang lebih tinggi, SAV yang berukur lima meter ini hadir dengan kelebaran yang bersaiz 2,000 mm, dan jarak roda (wheelbase) berukuran 3,105 mm.\n\n<p>Jarak kelegaan tanah mencecah 1,805 mm, iaitu 60 mm lebih tinggi berbanding BMW X5, sekali gus memberikan BMW X7 terbaharu sebuah pesona visual yang memukau. Di bahagian atas, jentera ini juga mengenakan rel bumbung yang â€˜sportyâ€™ dalam varian â€˜Aluminium Satinâ€™.\n\n\n\n<p>Dari belakang, kita dapat melihat saiz jentera ini yang menyingkap keluasan ruang kabin BMW X7 terbaharu. Siluet menegak di belakang juga ditakrifkan secara visual oleh lampu belakang berbentuk L yang langsing dan ia hadir dalam rekaan tiga dimensi yang menarik.\n\n<p>Pintu but belakang yang luas hadir dengan dua bahagian dan ia boleh dioperasikan secara elektrik. Tambahan lagi, BMW X7 yang pertama menampilkan dua paip ekzos segi empat yang besar di setiap sisi, ia menonjolkan karakter jentera ini yang gagah.\n\n<p>Enjin\n\n<p>SAV mewah ini hadir dalam varian BMW X7 xDrive40i Pure Excellence, dan ia dikuasakan oleh enjin petrol sebaris enam silinder yang memiliki kuasa maksimum berjumlah 250 kW/ 340 kk, dan puncak tork berjumlah 450 Nm. Justeru, jentera ini berupaya untuk membuat pecutan dari sifar ke seratus dalam masa 6.1 saat.\n\n<p>Kesemuanya dapat dikecapi dengan penggunaan bahan bakar gabungan yang berjumlah 9.5l/100 km dan emisi karbon gabungan berjumlah 217 g/km.\n\n<p>Daya kuasa disalurkan kepada empat roda jentera ini melalui transmisi Steptronic Sport lapan kelajuan. Sistem pacuan semua roda xDrive yang melengkapi SAV mewah ini pula memaksimumkan cengkaman, kelincahan dan stabiliti pengendalian yang berhubung dengan Kawalan Stabiliti Dinamik (â€œDynamic Stability Controlâ€ atau â€œDSCâ€) untuk mengasaskan aspek pengendalian yang cemerlang tidak kira apa jua kondisi cuaca atau jalan raya yang diharungi.\n\n\n\n<p>Reka bentuk casis yang penuh sofistikasi pada BMW X7 xDrive40i Pure Excellence ini merangkumi sebuah suspensi udara dwigandar. Oleh itu, ia memastikan jentera tersebut dapat menawarkan tahap keselesaan pemanduan yang lebih baik, dan pada masa yang sama, pilihan untuk melaraskan suspensi kereta ini setinggi 80 mm, dengan lima tetapan ketinggian yang berbeza.\n\n<p>Bukan itu sahaja, pemandu boleh melaras jarak kelegaan tanah dengan hanya menekan butang yang disediakan di ruang kokpit untuk menaikkan atau menurunkan ketinggiannya sebanyak 40 mm melepasi tetapan ketinggian standard, ia amat berguna untuk pemanduan luar jalan atau â€˜off-roadâ€™, serta untuk mengakses ruang but dengan lebih mudah.\n\n<p>Buat julung kali dalam model BMW X, BMW X7 xDrive40i Pure Excellence yang terbaharu ditawarkan bersama sistem suspensi, â€˜Executive Drive Proâ€™ dengan penstabilan guling aktif (active roll stabilisation) yang membekalkan sebuah kombinasi ideal antara keselesaan pemanduan dan dinamik yang bertaraf tinggi.\n\n<p>Penstabilan antiguling aktif mengurangkan kadar pergerakan badan serta inklinasinya ketika membelok ke tahap yang minimum. Keselesaan pemanduan dinaik taraf dengan sistem Kawalan Peredam Dinamik (Dynamic Damper Control) yang berupaya untuk memproses data daripada sistem navigasi serta kamera hadapan.\n\n<p>Kokpit futuristik\n\n<p>Ruang kabin jentera BMW X7 yang pertama ini membawakan elemen trim cantik buatan tangan â€œCrafted Clarityâ€ yang dipadankan ke atas tuil gear, pelaras bunyi pembesar suara, butang Mula/Henti dan Pengawal iDrive (iDrive Controller).\n\n\n\n<p>Berterapkan orientasi pemandu BMW yang tipikal dan posisi tempat duduk yang lebih tinggi dengan tahap visibiliti sempurna juga merupakan karakteristik yang membentuk model BMW X.\n\n<p>Kelengkapan yang lain meliputi stereng sport berkulit dan tempat duduk yang boleh dilaras secara elektrik dengan teknologi ventilasi. Permukaan trim kayu halus pula dibingkaikan dengan trim berelektrosadur pada panel instrumen serta konsol sentral untuk memperkayakan aura keelegenan bahagian interior.\n\n', 'BMW Live Cockpit Professional dengan sistem operasi, BMW Operating System 7.0 menjamin fungsi kawalan jentera ini dapat digunakan dengan lancar. Ia menggabungkan kluster instrumen digital 12.3 inci yang boleh dikonfigurasikan dengan Paparan Kawalan (Control Display) sentral yang mempunyai fungsi skrin sentuh serta antara muka (interface) yang tercanggih.\n\n<p>SAV mewah ini turut membawakan BMW Intelligent Personal Assistant yang dikawal dengan suara, ia dapat memahami pertuturan biasa, membantu melaksanakan fungsi pemanduan yang tertentu dan menjawab soalan mengenai kenderaan tersebut.\n\n\n\n<p>Kawalan Gestur BMW (BMW Gesture Control) juga kini dapat mengenal pasti dan memberi maklum balas kepada tujuh pergerakan tangan yang berbeza, termasuk pergerakan jari telunjuk dalam bentuk membulat mengikut arah jam untuk menaikkan bunyi pembesar suara, serta dengan mengibaskan tangan ke kanan untuk menolak panggilan telefon.\n\n<p>Elemen kemewahan dan serba kontemporari diwujudkan oleh pencahayaan ambien dengan fungsi Karpet Aluan (Welcome Carpet) yang bersertakan senario pencahayaan spesifik untuk situasi tertentu. Senario pencahayaan ini meliputi â€˜Welcomeâ€™ dan â€˜Goodbyeâ€™, serta pencahayaan yang terhasil setelah pintu dibuka atau ketika menerima panggilan telefon.\n\n<p>Tawaran menarik yang lain merangkumi penyaman udara lima zon, Sistem Bunyi Keliling Harman Kardon dengan 16 Pembesar suara, dan tirai gulung elektrik untuk tingkap sisi. Bukan itu sahaja, sistem â€˜Rear Entertainment Professionalâ€™ bakal menaik taraf pengalaman penumpang jentera ini, dua skrin yang terletak di ruang belakang kini boleh dioperasikan menggunakan sentuhan jari â€“ ia membekalkan elemen hiburan yang sama kualitinya untuk penumpang di hadapan dan di belakang.\n\n<p>Ciri mewah\n\n<p>Keluasan BMW X7 yang pertama ini juga diserlahkan dengan bumbung kaca Panoramik â€“ â€˜Sky Loungeâ€™ yang turut membawakan senario pencahayaan LED. SAV mewah ini hadir dengan tujuh tempat duduk yang boleh dilaras secara elektrik sebagai standard.\n\n<p>Tempat duduk barisan kedua juga boleh dilaras dari tempat duduk pemandu. Jika dipesan dalam versi enam tempat duduk, kenderaan ini didatangkan dengan dua tempat duduk berasingan yang selesa di barisan kedua, lantas memudahkan lagi akses bagi penumpang di barisan ketiga.\n\n<p>BMW X7 yang pertama juga menampilkan fungsi â€˜soft-closeâ€™ pada pintunya yang tidak memerlukan tekanan yang kuat untuk menutup kesemua pintu jentera ini. Di belakang, SAV mewah ini memiliki kompartmen muatan bersaiz 325 liter yang versatil dan ia boleh mencecah 2,120 liter sekiranya tempat duduk belakang dilipat.\n\n<p>Tempat duduk di barisan kedua kini mempunyai pembahagian 40/20/40 untuk memuatkan barangan besar, serta ia juga boleh dibahagikan 60/40 untuk mewujudkan ruang masuk dan keluar yang lebih selesa buat para penumpang.\n\n\n\n<p>Semua fungsi yang dibawakan oleh Driving Assistant Professional boleh dirangkapkan dengan satu perkataan, iaitu â€˜komprehensifâ€™. Ia merangkumi Amaran Pengeluaran Laluan (Lane Departure Warning), Amaran Penukaran Laluan (Lane Change Warning) dan amaran perlanggaran hadapan dengan intervensi brek.\n\n<p>Bantuan pengekalan laluan (lane keeping assistant) dengan perlindungan perlanggaran sisi aktif (active side collision protection) juga disediakan, berserta dengan bantuan stering dan kawalan laluan (steering and lane control assistant), amaran perentasan trafik di hadapan dan belakang serta pencegahan perlanggaran belakang.\n\n<p>Ciri-ciri keselamatan dimaksimumkan dengan Bantuan Hentian Kecemasan (Emergency Stop Assistant), Bantuan Mengelak (Evasion Aid), Amaran Perentasan (Crossroads warning) dengan fungsi pembrekan bandar (city braking function).\n\n<p>BMW X7 ditawarkan dalam tujuh warna menawan. Ia meliputi warna putih (Mineral White), hitam (Black Sapphire), versi kelabu â€˜Artic Greyâ€™ atau â€˜Sophisto Greyâ€™, biru (Phytonic Blue), perang (Terra Brown) dan gangsa (Vermont Bronze).\n\n<p>Upholsteri di ruang dalam ditawarkan dalam kemasan â€˜Black Leather Vernascaâ€™, â€˜Coffee Leather Vernascaâ€™ (tidak ditawarkan untuk versi kenderaan enam tempat duduk) dan â€˜Cognac Leather Vernascaâ€™ dipadankan dengan papan pemuka (dashboard) berwarna hitam, atau â€˜Canberra Beige Leather Vernascaâ€™ dipadankan dengan papan pemuka â€˜Mokkaâ€™.\n\n<p>Anggaran harga jualan (atas jalan, tanpa insurans, dan bersama penawaran BMW Group Malaysia bagi Waranti Perbatuan Tanpa Had Bertempoh 5 Tahun, Program Servis Berjadual Percuma dan Program Waranti Tayar BMW)', '2019-10-22 07:17:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(42, 'four_wheel', 13, 0, 'uploads/7028d98a62cf9128e0598fca0a28e40d.jpg', 'All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV Arrives In Malaysia', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Preibu ', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/1eb8f3012b758ff1405d77da677cef33.jpg', 'uploads/62959cde525cc5c309e11af0b5cb4bd4.jpg', 'uploads/21d26b856eec6b8af515193f6a76d0ec.jpg', 'null', 'All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV Arrives In Malaysia\n', 'The much-awaited All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV, designed to express refinement, excellence and French know-how, harmonises the perfect alchemy of power and refinement bringing together premium materials, craftsmanship and technological innovations expected from a premium SUV.\n\n<p>SM Nasarudin SM Nasimuddin, Group Executive Chairman & CEO, Naza Corporation Holdings Sdn Bhd said, â€œDesigned to be charismatic, muscular and sensual, the All-New DS 7 Crossback demonstrates personality instantly with its elegant touches that is sure to turn heads on the road.\n\n\n\n<p>The All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV is a premium SUV that comes with a competitive price without compromising the experience of the DS brand.â€\n\n<p>â€œThe All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV is a model we have been anticipating to introduce in Malaysia.\n\n<p>Its arrival signifies a new milestone for the DS brand in Malaysia, having come a long way since first stepping foot in MalaysÄ±a in 2013. To meet demands for DS vehicles here, a flagship DS Store stands resolute in Petaling Jaya, the first in SouthEast Asia to meet individual expectations of its discerning clientele.â€\n\n<p>â€œMalaysians with a taste for premium SUV will find that the DS 7 Crossback SUV meets their every need, and we are confident in making an impact in the premium C-segment SUV market with the entry of DSâ€™s proudest thoroughbred from a brand known worldwide for its exclusive and outstanding products and services,â€ he added.\n\n<p>Naza Euro Motors Sdn Bhd, the sole distributor for DS in Malaysia officially launched the All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV, which was unveiled by Laurence NoÃ«l, Head of ASEAN & CEO of Naza Automotive Manufacturing, Groupe PSA and Dato Nik Hamdan Nik Hassan, Deputy Group CEO, Automotive Group, Naza Corporation Holdings.\n\n<p>DS has always placed particular emphasis on the light signature of its vehicles, and it continues to be a key feature of their styling. Reflecting the best tradition of craftsmanship, considerable thought went into every detail of the DS 7 Crossback SUV and the materials used inside the car.\n\n\n\n<p>Extending from the dashboard to the door panels and from the consoles to the seats, passengers and driver will be encompassed in the same complete ambience.\n\n<p>On the exterior, the DS 7 Crossback SUV sports a muscular yet elegant look resulting in a more distinguished and sporty poise.\n\n<p>The horizontal chrome DS WINGS on the front face convey a sense of prestige with their strong, well balanced lines. The new diamond-effect gloss black grille sports a hexagonal surround of dynamic lines, with the DS emblem taking up a prominent stance in the centre.\n\n<p>The DS ACTIVE LED VISION system adapts in width and range to the road conditions and vehicle speed and is set in five lighting modes â€“Town Beam, Country Beam, Motorway Beam, Adverse Weather and High Beam â€“ for greater safety on the road.\n\n<p>Resembling faceted jewels, the LED modules of the DS ACTIVE LED VISION headlamps emit a purple light when DS 7 Crossback is unlocked, before pivoting progressively by 180 degrees to create a hypnotic visual effect.\n\n<p>The first is an 8-inch central touchscreen that manages the multimedia interface, the entire DS CONNECT offer, wireless charging and compatible with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto and Mirrorlink. The second is a 12.3-inch personalisable screen dedicated to the digital instrument cluster.\n\n\n\n', 'The Performance Line trim promises dynamic quality throughout, combining â€˜Basalt Blackâ€™ grained Alcantara interior with Carmine/Gold topstitching and the use of precious materials such as Aluminium for the pedals, instantly enveloping occupants in a hushed sporty atmosphere.\n\n<p>The toggle switches on the chrome-finished central console feature a â€˜Clous de Parisâ€™ guilloche trim finish, while an exclusive animated watch in partnership with B.R.M Chronographs, the B.R.M R180, sits majestically on the dashboard adding a touch of elegance infused with a sense of tradition.\n\n<p>The distinctive DS LOUNGE presents the top-of-the-range FOCAL ElectraÂ® HiFi audio system, a meticulously devised acoustic architecture composed of 14 speaker drivers carefully positioned around the passenger compartment.\n\n<p>DS 7 Crossback SUV is underscored by its powerful highly-efficient, high-torque internal combustion engines which produces 165hp at 6,000rpm and maximum torque of 240Nm from 1,400rpm with its 1.6-litre THP four-cylinder petrol engine.\n\n<p>Exceptional power is sent to the front wheels via a six-speed automatic transmission (EAT6), recording 220km/h top speed. The All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV also features a new Electric Impulse Auto Gear Control with Paddle Shift for a thrilling drive.\n\n<p>The DS 7 Crossback SUV rides on 19-inch Onyx Black alloy wheels wrapped in 235/50 tyres giving the DS 7 Crossback SUV a comfortable yet confident ride on the road.\n\n<p>A five-star EuroNCAP rating only bodes well for this sleek SUV, the DS 7 Crossback SUV boasts a myriad of safety equipment such as Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), Electronic Stability Program (ESP), Emergency Brake Assist (EBS), Electronic Brakeforce Distribution (EBD), Emergency Brake Assist (EBA), Anti-skid Regulation (ASR), Dynamic Stability Control (DSC), Driver Attention Warning, six airbags, ISOFIX anchor points and passenger detection system, and DS ACTIVE LED VISION â€“ all of which working effortlessly to ensure the safety of the driver and passengers at all times.\n\n<p>The All-New DS 7 Crossback SUV is priced at RM199,888 on-the-road without insurance that comes with a 5-Years Peace Of Mind warranty or up to 120,000km whichever comes first; 5-Years 24-hour Roadside Assistance and exclusive access to SkyLounge by NAZA at Subang Skypark.\n\n<p>Colour options are Nera Black, Pearl White, Absolute Red and Platinum Grey', '2019-10-22 07:15:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(43, 'four_wheel', 15, 0, 'uploads/b52c9b34fca15fbfd8d30c3fddb8d417.jpg', 'Ferrari Triumphs In 24 Hours Of Le Mans', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu ', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/d9a87eaa1521c9fd7ee74c58dc8274fb.jpg', 'uploads/bb49aa42654c27506f43698f0b7e9eea.jpg', 'uploads/899d5cd9238ac09439435ff4e9eeccdd.jpg', 'null', 'Ferrari has won the 24 Hours of Le Mans for the 36th time. The win was taken by the 488 GTE fielded by AF Corse and driven by Alessandro Pier Guidi, James Calado and Daniel Serra.\n\n', 'THE victory is the 27th class win for the Prancing Horse, in addition to nine outright wins, the first one clinched 70 years ago at the hands of Luigi Chinetti and Lord Selsdon in the 166 MM bodied by Touring.\n\n\n\n<p>This marks the first victory in the GTE-Pro class at Le Mans for the 488 GTE as indeed for all the three drivers involved. For Alessandro and James this rounds off the Super Season in the best possible manner.\n\n<p>The Ferrari and AF Corse team triumph had been missing since the 2014 season, when it was scooped by Toni Vilander, Giancarlo Fisichella and Gianmaria Bruni.\n\n<p>Ferrari also took a podium finish in the GTE-Am class thanks to the 488 GTE of JMW Motorsport driven by Jeff Segal, Wei Lu and Rodrigo Baptista.\n\n<p>GTE-Pro\n\n<p>In the GTE-Pro class, the 488 GTEs fielded by AF Corse, cars no. 71 and 51, the Risi Competizione no. 89 were driven respectively by Davide Rigon, Alessandro PierGuidi and Oliver Jarvis.\n\n<p>GTE-Am\n\n<p>Ferrari teams have frequently battled for podium finishes in this, the class for gentleman drivers.\n\n<p>Three teams in particular stood out: the 488 GTE no. 84 of JMW Motorsport, the 62 of Scuderia Corsa / WeatherTech Racing and the 61 of Clearwater Racing. Jeff Segal, Wei Lu and Rodrigo Baptista held a very fast pace throughout the race, constantly battling for the podium in the cars of Keating Motorsports and Team Project 1.\n\n', 'James Calado â€“ AF Corse #51\n\n<p>â€œWeâ€™ve been working hard for this. In the last six months a lot of preparation was made into this and I think this is something we were really wanting more than everything. It was not an easy race at all.\n\n<p>It was very up and down, with a few issues and after our sister car had an issue so we had to adapt and change a few things. It was great staff, very demanding but we did it and I am really happy for these guys. These are really super teammates, both very quick and we have an amazing team of people around us.â€\n\n\n\n<p>Alessandro Pier Guidi â€“ AF Corse #51\n\n<p>â€œIt was a very tough race. We had a great race, there are a lot of manufacturers so everyone can win and we had to push from the beginning to the end.\n\n<p>Being with the red racing suit on the podium listening to the Italian anthem is something special, and looking down seeing so many people is something that you cannot forget. I think we had the perfect race today both for us drivers and for the strategy set by the engineers.â€\n\n<p>Daniel Serra â€“ AF Corse #51\n\n<p>â€œItâ€™s unbelievable. I think I am a lucky guy to be at the right place in the right moment. Itâ€™s only my third time and I have won twice and thatâ€™s difficult to achieve. Itâ€™s really special to win in red, I have to say.\n\n<p>It is amazing and fantastic. I just drove and they did their job too. They drove amazingly. To watch everything, two guys wanting something so much; they were on a mission and it was nice to watch and to be able to help them.â€\n\n<p>Antonello Coletta â€“ Head of Ferrari AttivitÃ  Sportive GT\n\n<p>â€œAs we have said in the past, we just want to compete on equal terms with our rivals and that is just what happened in this edition of the 24 Hours of Le Mans.\n\n<p>We were able to give a display of how much talent there is in both this Ferrari and the fantastic AF Corse team. Alessandro Pier Guidi, James Calado and Daniel Serra were perfect and knew exactly how to maximize the strategy that our technical team and Amato Ferrariâ€™s men have developed so splendidly.\n\n<p>Iâ€™m extremely proud; we deserved to win this race in the GTE-Pro class once again, after such a long time, and to do it exactly 70 years after the first win in 1949 is also another reason to be happy.\n\n<p>We finish the season with a smile on our faces even though we were sorry to see the retirement of car 71 and we are very pleased with the results obtained in the GTE-Am class. What we have achieved in the race today will motivate us to give even more in preparation for the new season which gets underway in September.â€', '2019-10-22 07:14:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(44, 'two_wheel', 1, 0, 'uploads/4fb5f1800b171e082fed22d79c0f4f36.jpg', 'Mforce Bikes Holdings Launches SYM JET14 200 and SYM MIO 110 â€“ from RM7,888 and RM5,688', 8, 'News', 'Wahid Ooi Abdullah ', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/54eb6ab2d81d6ef3559e0dfb48d259c4.jpg', 'uploads/fd766820c8a95b06255d2c4cd6b93077.jpg', 'uploads/1bc209815f8769e5076c5774f72de1d4.jpg', 'null', 'Mforce Bikes Holdings Launches SYM JET14 200 and SYM MIO 110 â€“ from RM7,888 and RM5,688\n\nMforce Bikes Holdings Sdn. Bhd. launched the SYM JET14 200 and SYM MIO 110 scooters today.\nThe JET14 200 is equipped with ABS.\nThe MIO 110 features a large storage space.\nMforce Bikes Holdings Sdn. Bhd. launched the SYM JET14 200 and SYM MIO 110 scooters today.\n\nSYM scooters are already known in the Malaysian motorcycle market. Mforce are hopeful that these two new models will continue the brandâ€™s moment', 'SYM MIO 110\n\n<p>Just as the JET14 200 is a continuation of another model, the MIO 11 continues the MIO 110â€™s lineage.\n\n<p>The engine is electronically fuel injected and complies to Euro 3 standards.\n\n<p>Main features include a digital LCD screen and large underseat storage space. Itâ€™s equipped with a 160mm brake disc up front and a drum rear.\n\n<p>The bike is offered in Papermint (sic), Flamingo and Matte Black. The price of RM5,688 excludes SST and other fees.\n\n<p>Itâ€™s also covered by a two-year, 20,000km warranty.', 'Just as the JET14 200 is a continuation of another model, the MIO 11 continues the MIO 110â€™s lineage.\nThe engine is electronically fuel injected and complies to Euro 3 standards.\nMain features include a digital LCD screen and large underseat storage space. Itâ€™s equipped with a 160mm brake disc up front and a drum rear.\nThe bike is offered in Papermint (sic), Flamingo and Matte Black. The price of RM5,688 excludes SST and other fees.\nItâ€™s also covered by a two-year, 20,000km warranty.', '2019-10-19 14:19:54', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(46, 'four_wheel', 12, 0, 'uploads/6138d25acef9982370822cf5d79091fd.jpg', 'The Ferrari SF90 Stradale â€“ The New Series-Production Supercar', 1, 'News', 'Edit Oleh Prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/5247b5853fcb669ed3afac75144238a1.jpg', 'uploads/fb6810370f5adcfdf9068538e09a6e22.jpg', 'uploads/eaffcc4aa942fa91044e6ae711bc0e2e.jpg', 'MvVXL-vBQs0', 'The most powerful Prancing Horse car ever references Scuderia Ferrari\n\nFERRARI introduces a new chapter in its history with the introduction of its first series production PHEV (Plug-in Hybrid Electric Vehicle), the SF90 Stradale, images, videos and information on which can be seen on the dedicated web site: SF90stradale.com.\n\n', 'The new model is extreme on every level and represents a true paradigm shift, because it delivers unprecedented performance for a production car.\n\n<p>Figures such as 1,000 cv, and a weight-to-power ratio of 1.57 kg/cv, and 390 kg of downforce at 250 km/h not only put the SF90 Stradale at the top of its segment, but also mean that a V8 is the top-of-the-range model for the first time in the marqueâ€™s history.\n\n<p>The carâ€™s name encapsulates the true significance of all that has been achieved in terms of performance. The reference to the 90th anniversary of the foundation of Scuderia Ferrari underscores the strong link that has always existed between Ferrariâ€™s track and road cars.\n\n<p>A brilliant encapsulation of the most advanced technologies developed in Maranello, the SF90 Stradale is also the perfect demonstration of how Ferrari immediately transitions the knowledge and skills it acquires in competition to its production cars.\n\n\n\n<p>The SF90 Stradale has a 90Â° V8 turbo engine capable of delivering 780 cv, the highest power output of any 8-cylinder in Ferrari history.\n\n<p>The remaining 220 cv is delivered by three electric motors, one at the rear, known as the MGUK (Motor Generator Unit, Kinetic) due to its derivation from the Formula 1 application, located between the engine and the new 8-speed dual-clutch transmission on the rear axle, and two on the front axle.\n\n<p>This sophisticated system does not, however, make for a more complicated driving experience. Quite the opposite, in fact: the driver simply has to select one of the four power unit modes, and then just concentrate on driving.\n\n<p>The sophisticated control logic takes care of the rest, managing the flow of power between the V8, the electric motors and the batteries.\n\n\n\n<p>The SF90 Stradale is also the first Ferrari sports car to be equipped with 4WD, a step necessary to allow the incredible power unleashed by the hybrid powertrain to be fully exploited, ensuring the car has become the new benchmark for standing starts: 0-100km/h in 2.5 sec and 0-200km/h in just 6.7 seconds.\n\n<p>Ferrariâ€™s engineers were able to further broaden the spectrum of dynamic controls by introducing the full-electric front axle, known as the RAC-e (electronic cornering set-up regulator).\n\nAs well as exclusively providing propulsion in electric drive, the two front motors independently control the torque delivered to the two wheels, extending the concept of Torque Vectoring. Fully integrated into the carâ€™s vehicle dynamics controls, the RAC-e governs the distribution of torque, making driving on the limit much simpler and easier.\n\n\n\n<p>The introduction of this hybrid architecture was a challenge with regard to managing the additional weight which was resolved by an obsessive attention to detail and the overall optimisation of the whole of the car.\n\n<p>For maximum performance in terms of overall weight, rigidity and centre of gravity, the chassis and bodyshell of the SF90 Stradale is all new, built using multi-material technology, including, for example, carbon fibre.\n\n<p>The development of a hybrid car of this kind demanded the development of a series of innovative aerodynamic solutions.\n\n\n\n<p>The significant boost in the power unitâ€™s performance brought with it an increase in the amount of heat energy to be dissipated and required the development team to carry out an in-depth review of the aerodynamic flows on the radiating masses. It also demanded new solutions to increase downforce efficiently and guarantee maximum stability at all speeds and in all driving conditions.\n\n<p>Particularly noteworthy is the innovative shut-off Gurney, a patented active system located at the rear of the car which regulates the air flow over the upper body, reducing drag at high speeds with low lateral dynamics loads and increasing downforce in corners, under braking and during changes of direction.\n\n<p>The new car is epoch-changing from a stylistic perspective as it completely rewrites the mid-rear-engined sports berlinetta proportions introduced on the 360 Modena twenty years ago, instead taking its inspiration from Ferrariâ€™s recent supercars.\n\n<p>A good example is the cockpit, which has a smaller frontal section and is placed closer to the front of the car to reduce drag. This was also achieved without impacting on-board comfort.\n\n\n\n<p>The track-derived â€œeyes on the road, hands on the wheelâ€ philosophy takes on a truly central role for the first time too, significantly influencing the ergonomics and styling of the interior. The result is an HMI (Human-Machine Interface) and interior layout concept that are a complete departure from previous models.\n\n', 'Another major innovation is the steering wheel which now has a touchpad and a series of haptic buttons that allow the driver to control virtually every aspect of the car using just their thumbs. The central instrument cluster is now entirely digital with the first automotive application of a 16â€ curved HD screen which can be fully configured and controlled using the controls on the steering wheel.\n\n<p>On the central tunnel, improved ergonomics have been combined with an element from the past: the automatic gearbox controls are now selected by a grille-style feature that references Ferrariâ€™s legendary manual gear-shift gate. Thus past and present skilfully merge to point the new Ferrari towards the future.\n\n<p>The SF90 Stradale also sees the debut of the new ignition key with full keyless technology which will gradually be introduced across the rest of the range, personalised with the modelâ€™s name. Thanks to a special compartment in the central tunnel, it becomes an integral part of the carâ€™s styling.\n\n\n\n<p>In addition to the sporty version, which references the shape and colour of the signature rectangular Prancing badge sported by Ferrariâ€™s road cars, there will also be a more elegant metal-coloured version.\n\n<p>For the first time on a Ferrari, clients can choose between the standard car and a version with a more sports-oriented specification.\n\n<p>The Assetto Fiorano specification includes significant upgrades, including special GT racing-derived Multimatic shock absorbers, extra lightweight features made from high-performance materials such as carbon-fibre (door panels, underbody) and titanium (springs, entire exhaust line), resulting in a weight-saving of 30 kg.\n\n<p>Another difference is the high downforce carbon-fibre rear spoiler which generates 390 kg of downforce at 250 km/h. The Assetto Fiorano includes Michelin Pilot Sport Cup2 tyres designed specifically to improve performance on the track in the dry. They feature a softer compound and fewer grooves than the tyres provided as standard.', '2019-10-22 07:13:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(47, 'two_wheel', 16, 0, 'uploads/61f76b1cf6696c61bbdc68d7e67243a8.jpg', 'Here it is! The 2020 Triumph Street Triple RS!', 8, 'News', 'Wahid Ooi Abdullah', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/8d230d24be76714f108a6e3b689c89c4.jpg', 'undefined', 'undefined', 'null', 'Here it is! The 2020 Triumph Street Triple RS!', 'The 2020 Triumph Street Triple RS breaks cover.\nIts engine receives a power boost.\nIt also receives updated looks and lost some weight.\nThe 2020 Triumph Street Triple RS breaks cover after Triumphâ€™s teases over the last couple of months.\n\n<p>The new bike retains the Street Tripleâ€™s classic silhouette, but itâ€™s apparent that Triumph pared it down to look even more purposeful than ever. The headlamps were updated to look fiercer. There are new radiator flanks, exposing more of the frame. Triumphâ€™s scalpel pared away excess weight, ending up with a bike which weighs only 166 kg dry. The manufacturer claims that itâ€™s the lightest bike in its category.\n\n<p>Over to the engine. While the 2020 bike was revealed in preparation for Euro 5 emission, the engine gained power, courtesy of the lessons learned in Moto2 racing. (Triumph is the exclusive engine supplier to the championship.)\n\n<p>The three-cylinder architecture remains the same and includes two catalytic convertors. Despite that, it receives a 9-percent power boost. It now produces 121 bhp and 77.3 Nm of torque, compared to the previous 116 bhp and 76 Nm of torque. That doesnâ€™t appear to be a lot on paper, of course, but you can look forward to a punchier midrange combined with a more responsive throttle (the previous bikeâ€™s throttle was already super responsive and smooth!). The gains and smoother powerband are the courtesy of a new exhaust cam, besides the high precision machining of the crankshaft, clutch and balancer.\n\n', 'The previous RSâ€™s chassis and suspension are already in the ballpark, hence carried over to the new bike. The front forks remain the 41mm upside-down Showa BFF, while the rear mono shock is the Ohlins STX40.\nBraking duties are handled by a pair of Brembo M50 monobloc 4-piston callipers gripping a pair of 310mm discs up front and a Brembo single-piston calliper out back.\nAnd as we speculated, there is a new TFT screen armed with Bluetooth connectivity. Through the MyTriumph app, the rider can receive navigation prompts, manage music and calls and control his GoPro action camera. The five riding modes i.e. Track, Sport, Road, Rain and rider customisable are also enhanced.\nThe previous Triumph Street Triple RS remains the most fun bike weâ€™ve tested to this point, so we canâ€™t wait to test this new one!\n\n', '2019-10-19 14:18:48', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(48, 'four_wheel', 15, 0, 'uploads/87fb8f252b52944338d1b00495d6eb00.jpg', 'New Megane R S Trophy-R: Record At NÃ¼rburgring For The Best-Performing Model Ever Marketed By Renault', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor prebiu', '2019-10-08', 'uploads/34d148d0a1215780e208a4ad0da22830.jpg', 'uploads/611ad52561c6f75ab5c88dae09274354.jpg', 'uploads/c9c69926d9e1ee4def28cb1cd27d83b8.jpg', 'null', 'Renault presents MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R, a new version of a saga begun 15 years ago, that has set like its iconic forerunners a new record on the Nordschleife in front-wheel-drive production car category. It perpetuates Renault Sportâ€™s passion for challenge and performance.\n\n', 'COMPARED to the Megane R.S. Trophy, the Renault MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R, equipped with the same 300 hp engine, owes its increased speed to the weight reduction (up to 130 kg), the work on aerodynamics and the more radical development of its chassis for road holding.\n\n\n\n<p>The Renault MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R will be launched on the market before the end of 2019, as an exclusive limited edition of a few hundred units only.\n\n<p>Renault Sport has built on a partnership with some of the most recognised specialists in their disciplines: AkrapoviÄ, Brembo, Bridgestone, Ã–hlins and Sabelt.\n\n<p>MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R sets a 07â€™40â€™â€™100 new record on the Nordschleife 20.600 km lap, and a 07â€™45â€™â€™389 reference time on the official whole lap of 20.832 km.\n\n<p>With drivers from the Renault F1@ Team Daniel Ricciardo and Nico HÃ¼lkenberg behind the wheel, on 24 May in Monaco, on the fringes of the Formula One Grand Prix, the MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R will make its first physical appearance.\n\n\n\n<p>In the tradition of Renault Sport, this new generation of MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R does not only owe its performance to its pure power, since its 300 hp engine is that of Megane R.S. Trophy, launched in early 2019.\n\n<p>The MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R was developed as a racing car in a very short time, by a small dedicated team that operated in agile mode by focusing on three aspects: maximum weight reduction (up to 130 kg compared to the Megane R.S. Trophy excluding options), reworked aerodynamics and a more radical development of its drive axles.\n\n<p>The result is truly breath-taking: on 5 April, 2019, the MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R set a new officially approved record and reference time for the compact car segment of production cars on the Nordschleife of the NÃ¼rburgring, now a world-renowned race track and proving ground for cars and sports performance.\n\n<p>It covered the 20.600 km in 07â€™40â€™â€™100, and the official whole lap length of the Nordschleife 20.832 km in 07â€™45â€™â€™389.\n\n\n', '\nThe story of the Megane R.S. and the â€œRingâ€ has been going on for more than 10 years. It started in 2008 with the very first record in the front-wheel-drive production car category: Megane R.S. R26.R completed the lap in 8â€™17â€™â€™.\n\n<p>A time that was shattered 3 years later, in 2011, by the second generation Megane R.S. Trophy version, in the hands of the carâ€™s driver-builder, Laurent Hurgon (8â€™07â€97). In 2014, it passed under the 8-minute mark (7â€™54â€36) for the first time with the Trophy-R version of the Megane III R.S.\n\n<p>He was also the one who drove the latest generation of MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R to set this new reference time, in a chase for records in which gaining every second has become that much harder.\n\n<p>The MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R will be marketed before the end of 2019 as an exclusive limited edition of a few hundred units.\n\n<p>Renault F1@ Team drivers Daniel Ricciardo and Nico HÃ¼lkenberg will be behind the wheel when the MEGANE R.S. TROPHY-R makes its first public appearance on 24 May, 2019, the Friday before the FORMULA 1 GRAND PRIX DE MONACO.\n\n<p>Renault Sport has built on the solid support of privileged partners: AkrapoviÄ for the exhaust system, Brembo for the brakes, Bridgestone for the tyres, Ã–hlins for the shock absorbers and Sabelt for the bucket seats.\n\n<p>Nordschleife: a new official course length for lap times and records. Until this year, most of the lap times and so far unofficial records were registered on the 20.600 km course (start of lap time clocking at the end of the Nordschleife start/finish straight at T13, end of lap time clocking at the start/finish line at the beginning of the start/finish straight at T13).\n\n<p>From 2019, the official course formalized by the NÃ¼rburgring is the 20.832 km whole lap of the Nordschleife with start and end of lap time clocking at the start/finish line of the Nordschleife track. In this context, the Megane R.S. Trophy-R time is categorized in the compact cars class (only production vehicles with ECE approval without modifications).', '2019-10-22 07:12:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(51, 'four_wheel', 15, 0, 'uploads/dd0da5293769db7dc91bac9b57572d1c.jpeg', 'Pasukan R3 Proton Kuasai Pusingan 3 Siri Kejuaraan Malaysia (MCS)', 1, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu ', '2019-10-09', 'uploads/745c80b1490b79f4025013c659dad5d1.jpg', 'uploads/d8a2f3c55eaeb2c948fd69f10cf451f5.jpg', 'uploads/a67b10dba587b52caddbd60e3d1b263a.jpg', 'null', 'Dua kemenangan dan satu podium pada perlumbaan kedua kemuncak kemenangan Proton.\n\nPASUKAN PROTON R3 (R3) menguasai Pusingan 3 Siri Kejuaraan Malaysia (MCS) 2019 dengan merangkul kemenangan dua kali termasuklah mendapatkan tempat podium dengan menamatkan 1-2-3 dalam perlumbaan kedua', 'Perlumbaan diadakan di Litar Antarabangsa Sepang (SIC) pada hujung minggu lalu, dengan setiap perlumbaan dijalankan selama satu jam yang menguji ketahanan kereta serta pemandu dan akhirnya membuktikan sekali lagi bahawa R3 adalah pasukan yang paling menonjol bagi dalam kelas M-Pengeluaran.\n\n<p>Permulaan perlumbaan pada hujung minggu lalu tidak berpihak pada pasukan R3 kerana sesi kelayakan adalah tidak seperti yang dirancang.\n\n<p>Proton Suprima S yang dipandu oleh Mitchell Cheah layak di pole position tetapi rakan sepasukannya Fariqe Hairuman dan Syafiq Ali yang memandu Proton Iriz dan James Veerapen dalam Proton Saga hanya berjaya mendapat tempat keempat dan kelima pada grid permulaan di mana mereka terus berusaha mengawal pengendalian yang sempurna.\n\n\n\n<p>Semasa perlumbaan, Proton Suprima S yang dipandu oleh Mitchell menguasai perlumbaan itu dan mengambil bendera untuk memberikan R3 satu lagi kemenangan kelas M-Pengeluaran dalam kejuaraan 2019.\n\n<p>Dua lagi kereta R3 mengakhiri perlumbaan di tempat keempat dan kelima, membuatkan pasukan itu perlu berusaha dengan lebih keras bagi mencapai kemenangan seterusnya pada hujung minggu itu.\n\n', 'Perlumbaan kedua diadakan pada hari Ahad dan dengan kedudukan permulaan berdasarkan pada kedudukan penamat dari perlumbaan pertama, ketiga-tiga kereta lumba PROTON R3 bermula pada kedudukan pertama, keempat dan kelima.\n\n\n\n<p>Walau bagaimanapun, apabila lampu mula dinyalakan, ketiga-tiga kereta tersebut dengan pantas mendahului di mana prestasi unggul pada Proton Suprima S, Iriz dan Saga memberikan pasukannya satu perlumbaan yang tidak dapat ditandingi.\n\n<p>Dengan menguasai perlumbaan kedua, R3 mengambil peluang sendiri untuk memaksimumkan mata yang dikumpul oleh pasukan mereka yang mendahului.\n\n<p>Oleh itu, pada perlumbaan itu, Proton Iriz yang dipandu Fariqe dan Syafiq yang pertama tiba di garisan penamat diikuti Mitchell dengan Proton Suprima S dan James di dalam Proton Saga.\n\n<p>Ia adalah kali pertama R3 menamatkan perlumbaan di kedudukan tiga teratas dan keputusannya meninggalkan Fariqe dan Syafiq hanya dua mata di belakang pemenang kejuaraan terkini untuk kelas M-Pengeluaran dalam Siri Kejuaraan Malaysia 2019.', '2019-10-22 07:09:59', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(52, 'four_wheel', 14, 0, 'uploads/a785f8766d1f0de17ba843c36f89ab10.jpeg', 'Perodua Axia Tembusi Pasaran Seychelles', 2, 'News', 'Oleh Editor Prebiu ', '2019-10-09', 'uploads/0a721c09b7114363ed6157dd72ff876e.jpg', 'uploads/a0ff3c7b7ac79930b29241af14dd930d.jpeg', 'uploads/54bb665c0732e203dd165f491cec4570.jpeg', 'null', 'Perodua telah melancarkan Axia di Seychelles, menandakan kemasukan jenamanya ke negara kepulauan itu.\n\nPERODUA Axia dilancarkan di Hotel Eden Bleu, baru-baru ini, ditawarkan di sana dalam varian E MT, G, AT, SE dan AV, dengan harga promosi masing-masing 235,000 (*RM71,500), 265,000 (*RM80,600), 275,000 (*RM83,700) dan 290,000 (*RM88,300) Rupee Seychellois.', 'Semua varian dikuasakan oleh enjin 1.0 liter 1KR-VE dengan intelligent variable valve timing yang disambungkan kepada transmisi manual lima-kelajuan bagi varian E MT dan transmisi automatik empat-kelajuan bagi varian-varian yang lain.\n\n<p>â€œKami sangat teruja untuk mengeksport kenderaan kami ke Seychelles kerana ia memberi peluang kepada kami untuk memperkenalkan jenama Perodua kepada masyarakat berbilang bangsa yang berkunjung ke negara ini untuk bercuti.\n\n<p>â€œKami percaya bahawa ini akan memanfaatkan pasaran eksport masa hadapan kami,â€ kata\nPengarah Urusan Perodua Sales Sdn Bhd Datoâ€™ Dr Zahari Husin.\n\n<p>Perodua telah melantik SF Hybrid Motors Pty Ltd sebagai pengedar rasminya di Seychelles bagi mengendalikan jualan dan lepas jualan di sana.\n\n<p>â€œPerodua dan SF Hybrid Motors baru-baru ini telah menandatangani Memorandum Persefahaman bagi memasarkan model Perodua di Seychelles kepada pembeli individu dan fleet,â€ katanya.\n\n<p>Di benua Afrika, Perodua juga mengeksport ke Mauritius, di mana lebih 3,000 unit kenderaannya telah dijual sejak 1996.\n\n\n', '\nâ€œKami akui bahawa prestasi eksport kami masih tidak signifikan pada masa ini, namun kami gigih berusaha untuk mengembangkan perniagaan kami.\n\n<p>â€œKami sedang bekerjasama dengan rakan teknikal dan teknologi kami, Daihatsu Motor Company of Japan, dengan memanfaatkan pengalaman dan rangkaian mereka untuk merancangkan eksport yang lebih mampan dan menguntungkan,â€ katanya lagi.\n\n<p>Beliau menambah bahawa Seychelles adalah destinasi popular bagi pelancong Eropah dan Afrika dan ini akan membuka lebih banyak peluang eksport melalui pendedahan jenama Perodua.\n\n<p>â€œKami amat berbesar hati untuk membawa Perodua ke Seychelles. Kami percaya kepada Perodua dan oleh itu kami menawarkan waranti tiga tahun sehingga 100,000 km. Perodua Axia amat sesuai untuk pasaran Seychelles â€“ ia menawarkan gaya, keselamatan, ciri-ciri pintar serta kos pemilikan, servis dan alat ganti yang rendah,â€ kata Pengarah SF Hybrid Motors Christophe Larue.\n\n<p>Seychelles adalah sebuah negara kepulauan yang terdiri daripada 115 pulau di Lautan Hindi, sebelah timur daratan Afrika.', '2019-10-22 07:08:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0);
